Time is up. Its over in a blink of an eye. Guys i have only been with u for 2 yrs, but it seems like eternity. And i wish it would be. I love you guys so much...even though we will probably not stay friends forever, ill never forget you. Think about it...im not giving up on us, but we are all separate. and what is there to talk about separated? we arent all in the same school so why would we really care cause it doesnt affect us. Its sad knowing that we will fade out. But you guys will always be a part of me. Love you guys forever.

Hi guys! Well I kno some people are getting tired of writing in their journal about stuff people already kno, and no one commenting. So why dont we have this journal for other people, and then have our own personal journal, that only us can read, so we can help eachother with issues. That way we would get comments. Just us. Like the people who have it now, but make it friends only, so only we can read it, no one else. Si? Lemme kno what yall think...
